316
00:26:12,300 --> 00:26:13,020
Really?

317
00:26:13,170 --> 00:26:14,320
Yes.

318
00:26:15,480 --> 00:26:16,260
You know about this too?

319
00:26:16,380 --> 00:26:16,900
Of course!

320
00:26:19,240 --> 00:26:19,820
Yes.

321
00:26:21,440 --> 00:26:22,400
Alright.

322
00:26:22,960 --> 00:26:27,180
I'll send you any updates I have.

323
00:26:27,680 --> 00:26:29,080
To whom?

324
00:26:43,560 --> 00:26:45,760
Thank you, Mr. Parinth.

325
00:26:45,920 --> 00:26:47,560
I was so scared.

326
00:26:49,420 --> 00:26:50,240
So?

327
00:26:51,020 --> 00:26:52,640
Send updates to whom?

328
00:26:54,480 --> 00:26:55,660
To...

329
00:26:57,540 --> 00:26:58,720
my mom!

330
00:26:59,100 --> 00:27:01,480
She's worried about me.

331
00:27:04,530 --> 00:27:05,940
I'll go prepare the food for you.

332
00:27:20,080 --> 00:27:20,880
Not from me.

333
00:27:21,160 --> 00:27:21,660
From him.

334
00:27:52,360 --> 00:27:55,740
Parinth: Check this for me. I want it in ten minutes.

335
00:28:35,300 --> 00:28:36,140
It's not done yet?

336
00:28:38,460 --> 00:28:39,820
Too much.

337
00:28:40,400 --> 00:28:41,280
Are you saying I'm being too much?

338
00:28:41,960 --> 00:28:42,980
No.

339
00:28:43,380 --> 00:28:46,680
I mean it's a lot of work to do

340
00:28:46,900 --> 00:28:48,520
Please give me some time.

341
00:28:58,900 --> 00:29:00,200
You haven't eaten yet?

342
00:29:01,500 --> 00:29:03,480
When can I go eat?

343
00:29:04,440 --> 00:29:05,920
If I go, the work won't get done.

344
00:29:06,880 --> 00:29:08,240
Order something to eat if you're hungry.

345
00:29:08,780 --> 00:29:09,420
I'm leaving.

346
00:29:10,450 --> 00:29:10,960
Okay.

347
00:29:11,740 --> 00:29:12,500
Drive safely.

348
00:29:28,320 --> 00:29:29,360
The door is locked.

349
00:29:31,560 --> 00:29:32,220
Oh?

350
00:29:34,000 --> 00:29:35,980
I don't have a key either.

351
00:29:37,560 --> 00:29:38,700
Hmm.

352
00:29:39,320 --> 00:29:41,880
I'll call the building staff.

353
00:29:56,380 --> 00:29:58,080
No answer.

354
00:30:03,260 --> 00:30:04,140
Forget it.

355
00:30:07,340 --> 00:30:09,200
You're not going back?

356
00:30:10,040 --> 00:30:11,080
How can I go back? The door is locked.

357
00:30:20,520 --> 00:30:21,820
Are you hungry too?

358
00:30:25,000 --> 00:30:26,720
I'll find something for you to eat.

359
00:30:33,580 --> 00:30:35,140
Instant noodles for you, Mr. Parinth.

360
00:30:37,380 --> 00:30:39,060
I don't eat instant noodles.

361
00:30:41,220 --> 00:30:42,240
Mr. Parinth.

362
00:30:43,000 --> 00:30:44,140
You should eat something when you're hungry.

363
00:30:44,180 --> 00:30:45,580
There's nothing left in the carbinet.

364
00:30:46,000 --> 00:30:47,200
The housekeeper probably got rid of everything.

365
00:30:48,060 --> 00:30:49,720
Let's eat it before it gets cold.

366
00:30:50,860 --> 00:30:51,940
I have 'cat tongue.'

367
00:30:52,460 --> 00:30:53,140
What?

368
00:30:56,380 --> 00:30:57,960
I can't eat anything that is too hot.

369
00:31:00,880 --> 00:31:01,920
I see.

370
