You're drinking beer?

375
00:32:14,360 --> 00:32:15,120
Er...

376
00:32:21,980 --> 00:32:23,380
It's not mine.

377
00:32:32,100 --> 00:32:32,900
Do you have more?

378
00:33:08,720 --> 00:33:10,220
It's okay, Mr. Parinth.

379
00:33:11,700 --> 00:33:12,900
I can do it myself.

380
00:33:14,440 --> 00:33:16,100
I had already been through this work before you.

381
00:33:18,400 --> 00:33:20,220
Whoa, Mr. Parinth!

382
00:33:21,160 --> 00:33:23,160
If you did it before,

383
00:33:23,400 --> 00:33:25,660
why didn't you do it properly?

384
00:33:26,380 --> 00:33:29,920
Do you know that it's so hard to understand?

385
00:33:48,380 --> 00:33:49,360
Mr. Parinth.

386
00:33:51,960 --> 00:33:54,560
You work so hard,

387
00:33:55,820 --> 00:33:58,340
