388
00:33:58,740 --> 00:34:00,860
You should find something else to do.

389
00:34:05,940 --> 00:34:06,800
Like what?

390
00:34:08,120 --> 00:34:08,940
Like...

391
00:34:09,600 --> 00:34:12,340
find someone who understands you.

392
00:34:15,200 --> 00:34:16,460
I'm not interested in romance.

393
00:34:18,260 --> 00:34:19,300
Well then.

394
00:34:20,220 --> 00:34:22,840
So what are your interests?

395
00:34:26,020 --> 00:34:26,640
This.

396
00:34:27,700 --> 00:34:28,580
I'm interested in work.

397
00:34:32,680 --> 00:34:34,080
Come on.

398
00:34:35,380 --> 00:34:37,660
This is so boring, Mr. Parinth.

399
00:34:51,020 --> 00:34:52,100
Do you think...

400
00:34:54,040 --> 00:34:55,400
I'm a good leader?

401
00:34:55,720 --> 00:34:57,000
You?

402
00:34:58,000 --> 00:34:59,480
You're fierce like a tiger.

403
00:35:00,300 --> 00:35:03,720
You assign tons and tons of work.

404
00:35:03,720 --> 00:35:05,900
