405
00:35:05,900 --> 00:35:09,060
I know that you want the work to come out perfect.

406
00:35:09,060 --> 00:35:11,020
You want the company to thrive.

407
00:35:11,020 --> 00:35:12,360
But...

408
00:35:14,040 --> 00:35:17,320
