409
00:35:20,060 --> 00:35:23,360
I like seeing you focus on work.

410
00:35:24,800 --> 00:35:27,000
Mr. Parinth, you're my idol.

411
00:35:43,520 --> 00:35:44,380
What about...

412
00:35:44,860 --> 00:35:46,220
