416
00:36:06,140 --> 00:36:07,800
I actually don't know where to start.

417
00:36:13,280 --> 00:36:16,160
I don't know where to start too.

418
00:36:17,640 --> 00:36:18,600
But...

419
00:36:23,620 --> 00:36:26,020
I want you to try first.

420
00:36:28,700 --> 00:36:29,440
Try?

421
00:36:30,260 --> 00:36:31,500
Try what?

422
00:36:33,420 --> 00:36:36,460
You can try eating out with others.

423
00:36:37,160 --> 00:36:38,920
Try to socialize more.

424
00:36:39,080 --> 00:36:40,660
It's not that hard.

425
00:36:40,860 --> 00:36:43,180
But I understand that there's always a first time for everything.

426
00:36:45,080 --> 00:36:46,440
Mr. Parinth,

427
00:36:47,620 --> 00:36:49,760
you're my first...

428
00:36:52,200 --> 00:36:53,140
Your first?

429
00:36:55,260 --> 00:36:56,400
You mean...

430
00:36:59,400 --> 00:37:02,580
You're my first boss!

