00:37:03,600 --> 00:37:04,420
First!

432
00:37:04,880 --> 00:37:06,480
You're drunk.

433
00:37:16,760 --> 00:37:17,540
I'm not.

434
00:37:28,520 --> 00:37:29,160
First.

